---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — Timo Srinarmwong"
  description="Applied AI engineer in New York. Three years across Meta, Snorkel AI, and frontier-lab programs via Mercor."
>
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I&rsquo;m Timo Srinarmwong, an applied AI engineer in New York.
          For the last three years I&rsquo;ve worked on evals, fine-tuning,
          RLHF and SFT data pipelines, and agents: at Meta, at Snorkel AI,
          and on frontier-lab programs via Mercor.
        </p>
        <p>
          I&rsquo;m a native Thai speaker, which mattered on the project
          I&rsquo;m proudest of: fine-tuning Meta&rsquo;s production LLM for
          Thai, where the evaluation could not hide from me. On my own time
          I shipped GOLDI, a solo iOS app, to roughly 15,000 downloads with
          zero paid acquisition, then shut it down eleven months later when
          the retention data said to.
        </p>
        <p>
          I&rsquo;m open to full-time applied AI roles in New York or
          remote. The fastest way to reach me is email:
          <a href="mailto:tsrinarmwong.careers@gmail.com">tsrinarmwong.careers@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Swap the .art panel for a real photo:
           <img src="/images/portrait.jpg" alt="Timo Srinarmwong" /> -->
      <figure class="frame portrait">
        <div class="art portrait-art"></div>
        <figcaption class="meta">New York, NY</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-block: 4rem 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .portrait {
    width: min(14rem, 60%);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .portrait-art {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    --art-a: var(--pastel-sky);
    --art-b: var(--pastel-rose);
    --art-c: var(--pastel-cream);
  }

  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .about-grid {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-text {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .portrait {
      flex: 0 0 13rem;
      width: auto;
      /* Sits slightly into the right margin, like a print pull-out. */
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
